events.name: USC Trojans at Washington State Cougars

headlines.description: Luke Falk threw for 340 yards and two touchdowns, Erik Powell kicked a 32-yard field goal with 1:40 left, and No. 16 Washington State beat No. 5 USC 30-27 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Pullman Party: No. 16 Washington State beats No. 5 USC 30-27

video.headline: Washington State wins thriller over USC

events.name: Miami Hurricanes at Duke Blue Devils

headlines.description: Malik Rosier threw two touchdown passes and ran for another score and No. 14 Miami's defense shut down Duke in a 31-6 victory Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Rosier, defense help No. 14 Hurricanes top Blue Devils 31-6

events.name: Nebraska Cornhuskers at Illinois Fighting Illini

headlines.description: Quarterback Tanner Lee threw for 246 yards and three touchdowns, helping lead Nebraska to a 28-6 win over Illinois on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Lee throws 3 TDs, Nebraska rolls past Illinois 28-6

video.headline: Morgan stiff-arms his way into end zone
